  abstract={The article reveals the impact of the development of mobile communication technologies on the transformation of a digital product. Based on the disclosure of consistently changing technologies and mobile communication standards, the technological reasons for the evolution of the value of digital products are substantiated. Based on the changes in the key services of mobile communication networks of the fifth and sixth generations, the principles of expanding product and functional capabilities of production, new concepts of the essence of digital services and products are formulated. The substantiation of the system transformation of the production of products in physical and virtual environments in accordance with the needs of people and devices allowed us to reveal the essence and forms of multi-spatial future products produced and implemented in the meta-space at the merger of the physical and virtual worlds.},
